Author: Dmas111527
Subject: Failed me
Body:
It took me to streets that were closed! My kids had a field trip, and the 101 fwy was closed in Santa Barbara. I already knew this, so I wanted to make sure I leave early enough to take whatever detours I had to take. Google maps said I would make it in 2.5 hours, and showed that I'd be using side streets where the fwy was closed. I checked Waze (another GPS app) and that said it would take me 3.5 hours, taking me the 5 fwy route.  So I opted for Google Maps, the faster one, the so-called "trusted" GPS app, that would get me there 1 hour sooner than Waze's route.  We left early, and when we reached the part where the fwy was closed, it detoured me to streets that were closed off! Tried other streets, all closed!! I then used Waze, to see if there was another way, and Waze said I would have to go all the way around, through the 5 fwy. That would take me 4 hours from where I was! We obviously didn't make it to our field trip and ended up just going to a park in Santa Barbara, then headed back home. I should have used Waze from the beginning. Google Maps fail!

I've had prior issues with Google Maps before, like, it routing me in loops and circles, but never thought too much about it. It is the most used GPS app, so I thought it was the best. Nope. This time it pushed my buttons. Deleted the app.

Use Waze everyone! It's real time, with real users!

Author: Zaijialahagane
Subject: 评论可用
Body:
谷歌地图是 Google 公司提供的电子地图服务，包括局部详细的卫星照片。此款服务可以提供含有政区和交通以及商业信息的矢量地图、不同分辨率的卫星照片和可以用来显示地形和等高线地形视图。
在2014年3月5日谷歌表示印度22个城市的用户已经可以访问谷歌地图中75个在当地比较流行的室内场地地图，包括位于古尔冈的Ambience Mall，以及德里的Select City Walk购物中心等。
Translated Body: Google Maps is an electronic map service provided by Google that includes locally detailed satellite photos. This service provides vector maps with political and traffic and business information, satellite photos of different resolutions, and terrain and terrain views that can be used to display topography and contour lines. On March 5, 2014, Google said users in 22 cities across India have been able to access 75 of the more popular indoor venues on Google Maps, including Ambience Mall in Gurgaon and Select City Walk in Delhi. .

Author: waynepruski
Subject: Google Maps is nearly perfect, Lacks Speed and Speed Limit
Body: Google Maps is nearly perfect. Voice commands just “work” and 99.9% of the time it nails the correct destination and best route(s). If Google wanted to go for perfection, add current Speed of the vehicle and posted Speed Limit. This would make us drivers more aware to make an informed decision to decrease speed - it would SAVE LIVES.  I know it’s possible because other nav apps have this feature. And I know Google wouldn’t be so evil as to withhold this feature because it might infringe on State’s revenue generating schemes (which count on people being unaware of speed and take action, to heck with safety, right? It’s about money!)

Author: ナウい殿様
Subject: アプデ後に不調×××
Body:
仕事でGoogleナビを使ってますが、先日アプデしたらナビが調子悪くなりました…
まず、目的地を設定した後にナビ開始をタップしても反応せずスタートしません。
5，6回ほどタップしてやっとスタートになりますが1タップでは無反応です。(アプデ前は1タップでスタートしました)
また、経路どおりに走行してるのに、なぜかルートの再検索が多くなりました。最短ルートの再検索ならいいのですが遠回りのルートを案内したりします。おかげでUターンも増えました。
あと、地図表示のカラーパターンを自動にしていて、今までは夕方薄暗くなると夜間画面に変わりましたが、夜になっても日中画面のままの時があります。夜道の走行中にそのうち画面は変わりますが、日中画面のままだと明るくて運転しづらいです。
端末自体(iPhone8)は何も不具合ありません。
改悪ではなく改善をお願いします。
Translated Body: Although I am using Google Navi at work, Nabi got sick when I made the appointment the other day ... First of all, even if I tap on the start of navigation after I set the destination I will not react and will not start. I tap about 5 or 6 times and finally start, but 1 tap is not responsive. (I started with 1 tap in front of the ape.) Moreover, although I ran along the route, somehow I re-searched for the route somehow. I hope to re-search for the shortest route, but I will guide you around the detour route. Thanks to that, U turns also increased. Also, the color pattern on the map display is automatic, and until now it turned into a night screen if it gets dark in the evening, but there is a daytime screen even when it is night. The screen will change during the course of the night road, but it is hard to drive because it is bright when it is daytime screen. There is nothing wrong with the terminal itself (iPhone 8). Improve rather than worse, please.

Author: 扣子扣子000
Subject: 好用 据说很好用
Body:
应该是很好用 现在不知道大陆能不能用呢 顺利有序进行，保证实习学生的人身安全，根据国家及学校有关主管部门的规定，特制定本守则。

1. 严格遵守国家法律法令，严格遵守实习纪律及实习单位的保卫、安全操作规程、保密等一切规章制度和劳动纪律。特别要注意安全，杜绝各类不安全事故的发生。

2. 尊重实习单位的领导和职工，服从安排，听从指挥。实习期间一般不得请假，病假要有医生证明。若有特殊情况，必须向实习单位和学院指导教师请假。

3. 严格遵守作息制度，不得无故缺勤、迟到和早退；不得安排与实习无关的参观，更不得擅自离开单位外出游山玩水。外出活动应结伴而行，行为举止要文明礼貌，严禁酗酒闹事、打架斗殴、参与赌博以及其他不文明行为。

4. 实习学生应注意着装要求，根据特定的实习环境和实习单位的要求着装，严禁穿着不符合安全要求的服装鞋帽进入实习场地。

5. 学生在实习期间未经指导教师允许，不得到与实习工作无关的场所活动，不得到污染严重不宜于身心健康的环境逗留。不独自外出，不到行人稀少，偏僻危险的地方，不深夜滞留在外。

6. 严格遵守各种仪器设备操作规程，未经允许严禁乱触乱摸各类设备及动力、电力开关，以免造成事故。

7. 严格遵守岗位责任制，不串岗。未经允许，不得随意开动他人机器设备。严禁无证驾驶、操作机动车辆、施工机械。

8. 严禁在工地、厂房、车间等禁火处吸烟，注意用火安全，严防火灾事故发生。注意用电安全，不私接电源，不超负荷用电。

9. 生产中应加强自我保护意识。必须按照安全生产要求穿戴安全帽、警示服等安全保护装备，对于应配备安全防护装备而未配备的工作任务，应当拒绝。

10. 保持工作场地周围整洁，不准杂乱堆物，防止绊倒、滑跌、砸伤等危险发生。严禁在施工现场嬉戏打闹。

Subject: A good app but why can’t I rename custom locations?
Body:
So I travel a lot and while this app is nice to use some things truly frustrate me. 

For example:

1. Location is sometimes way off or will freeze/lag for no reason (I have full signal, good battery and no other apps open). 

2. I can’t name custom locations, only label them which doesn’t always work. I’ll go into my favourites and all my locations/places are named as longitude and latitude. And I cannot rename them at all, only assign them labels which don’t show up when viewing favourites etc. Which means I have to tap each location to figure out why I saved it.

Author: stonetcrab
Subject: 什么时候可以用在中国大陆
Body:
谷歌方面表示：“There have been no changes to Google Maps in China.（Google地图在中国没有任何变化）”。
另外，高德地图也已经否认了合作传闻，称根据政府的相关政策，高德地图没有计划与谷歌地图进一步合作。至于谷歌方面在是没有回应。
日本媒体报道称，谷歌公司为谷歌地图网站专门搭建了一个中国版本，并为中国iPhone用户推出了一个地图app。当用户使用谷歌地图内的导航功能时，将会自动跳转至高德地图，而谷歌地图将不会支持应用内导航服务。
从多方面获悉，谷歌也是积极回归中国市场。2017年底谷歌中国开发者大会上，谷歌云首席科学家李飞飞在演讲中宣布成立谷歌AI中国中心，中心落地北京。业内认为，谷歌正以AI之名强化在中国的业务。
Translated Subject: When can be used in mainland China
Translated Body: Google said: "There have been no changes to Google Maps in China." In addition, the high German map has also denied cooperation rumors, according to the government's relevant policies, high German map there is no plan to further cooperation with Google Maps. As for Google is no response. Japanese media reported that Google has created a Chinese version of the Google Maps site and launched a map app for Chinese iPhone users. When users use the navigation features within Google Maps, they automatically jump to Goode map, which will not be supported on Google Maps. In many ways, Google is also actively returning to the Chinese market. At the Google China Developers Conference at the end of 2017, Google Chief Scientist Li Feifei announced in the speech the establishment of Google AI China Center, the center of which is located in Beijing. The industry believes that Google is strengthening the business in China in the name of AI.

Body: Google Maps allows locals to be ‘guides’ in that they can help tourists and even locals discover and have improved-visits and experiences by allowing ‘guides’ leave reviews, locations, hours, both the positives and negatives of everything from restaurants to fast-food to outlet malls to museums and even health/medical clinics and hospitals. No one is too well-informed: we all co-exist and we can all improve our amazing areas we live and vacation and even perhaps drive through on the way to a more-distant location.

If this isn’t resolved soon, I will likely explore my other options.

Author: Leon Biggs
Subject: Was great, but is about as good as my Mum’s navigation...hopeless!
Body:
Used to love everything about this app and still has some top features like traffic and street view, but navigating anywhere is now a lottery if you get there as it pauses, freezes, sends you back to where you’ve came from, or can’t find one’s current location only where you started the journey! 9/10 of my last journeys it has wanted to send me the wrong way! I leave it on for traffic purposes and luckily know where I’m going but feel for anyone needing it to get them to their desired destination in my city at the moment as they’ll be sent on a wild Goose-chase!
Come on Google, return to your past glories again and fix these annoying issues or my Garmin will be pulled out of its retirement drawer!! 😡

Author: /\/\/\ ALP /\/\/\
Subject: Has been
Body:
Google maps used to be the best. 

It sometimes tries to do smt else than what I want it to do. Eg. Instead of showing results on the small map area I search in, it zooms out to show “more” results and “omit the results in the area searched”. 

It occasionally sent me to wrong locations. A Caltrain station was shown in the mountains, luckily I knew it could not be there and turned around to park and figure it out myself on Safari. 

UI is small and hard to read when driving, Apple maps is bigger and easier to use. 

It has annoying notifications constantly telling me to keep the app open so it can “update” offline maps. Very. Annoying. Who writes this software to nag the user every day?

In the past, Google tricked me to update the app, only to delete the already installed app and then refuse to reinstall the app, telling me to update my iOS to the latest version, which my phone’s hardware would not be able to handle. Dumb Google’s dumb software engineer could not do any better? How come they don’t check the iOS version before attempting to update? This lead to my initiation to Apple Maps and I never went back to Google Maps. 

Google reviews (for shops etc) is almost as bad as Apple maps’ Yelp, which heavily censors ratings and is very misleading. Google reviews sometimes removes ratings as well, but is not as manipulative as Yelp. 

Google maps has offline maps, handy when traveling, esp. internationally. Apple maps does not have that (yet). 

Overall, Google maps is overtaken by Apple maps, which has equally good info and directions, but better UI. 

I use Apple maps for everyday errands, but keep google maps as a back up and for restaurant reviews and offline maps.

Author: zoroark2018
Subject: 评论
Body: 《精灵宝可梦》，另有常见非官方译名：《口袋妖怪》(中国大陆译名)、《宠物小精灵》(中国香港译名)、《神奇宝贝》（中国台湾译名），是由Game Freak和Creatures株式会社开发，任天堂发行的系列游戏，是精灵宝可梦媒体作品的主要部分。最初的作品是在1996年于日本发行的Game Boy角色扮演游戏。精灵宝可梦系列一直贯穿任天堂的各代掌机之中。系列中的游戏通常成对发售（有所区别），复刻版常出现在初版游戏发布的几年后。游戏的主系列由角色扮演类游戏组成，旁支系列的游戏则包含有其他的类型，例如动作角色扮演游戏、益智游戏和电子宠物等。
Translated Body: "Pokemon", and other common unofficial translation: "Pokemon" (Chinese translation), "Pokemon" (Hong Kong, China translation), "Pokémon" (Taiwan translation of China) by Game Freak and Developed by Creatures Inc. and released by Nintendo, it is a major part of Pokemon Media's work. The original work was a Game Boy cosplay game released in Japan in 1996. Pokemon series has been running through all generations of Nintendo handheld. The games in the series are usually sold in pairs (somewhat different), and the remakes often appear a few years after the release of the first game. The main series of games consists of role-playing games, while the series of side-by-side games include other types such as action role playing games, puzzle games, and electronic pets.

钢结构应研究高强度钢材，大大提高其屈服点强度；此外要轧制新品种的型钢，例如H型钢（又称宽翼缘型钢）和T形钢以及压型钢板等以适应大跨度结构和超高层建筑的需要。
另外还有无热桥轻钢结构体系，建筑本身是不节能的，本技术用巧妙的特种连接件解决了建筑的冷热桥问题；小桁架结构使电缆和上下水管道从墙里穿越，施工装修都方便。

Steel is characterized by high strength, light weight, the overall stiffness is good, good deformation capacity, it is particularly suitable for the construction of large-span and ultra-high, super heavy type of buildings; material homogeneity and isotropic, is an ideal elastomer , Most in line with the basic assumptions of general engineering mechanics; material plasticity, good toughness, may have greater deformation, can withstand dynamic loads well; construction period is short; its high degree of industrialization, high degree of mechanization can be specialized production. Steel structure should be high-strength steel research and greatly enhance the yield point strength; In addition to the new varieties of steel rolling, such as H-beam (also known as wide-flange steel) and T-shaped steel and the pressure plate to meet the large-span structure and The need for super tall buildings. In addition there is no heat bridge light steel structure system, the building itself is not energy-saving, the technology uses ingenious special connectors to solve the building's hot and cold bridge problems; small truss structure so that the water pipes and plumbing through the wall, construction Decoration is convenient.

Author: F. Parsay
Subject: Unending Creativity
Body:
We are in a world with interconnected conditions and interdependent living beings and we can see that Google Maps is always finding and communicating the realities that are present and also constantly moving at and changing for the future. We witness their powerful transforming practices which brings with it important innovations and insights. Their experiential learning and gathering data from the real situations is a great help in finding successful navigation solutions. What a joy to be a witness and to benefit from their unending creativity and their efforts towards achieving their goals and creating a better life for all.

Farinaz Parsay

Author: Dizkoteck
Subject: Totally regret updating
Body: What was once the dominant app for directions is now a death trap waiting to happen. I loved google maps but the last update changed it all. When you put in directions and zoom out it now automatically zooms back in. Why? I want to have an visual of how far the destination is. And can you please stop giving alternate directions while I'm driving and have chosen a route. There are two highlighted routes! Do I exit here or the next one? And for god sakes drop automatic direction change in the middle of the route. If you're telling me go straight I'll go straight but don't tell me at the last second to from the left lane to right exit 300 ft away. The previous version had one of this.

Author: P.Dow
Subject: I don't leave home without it!!!!!
Body: Google maps is always a part of my vacations. I live in Europe right now, and any trip we go on always involves driving, public transportation, cycling or walking. As long as we take the time to download area maps and review our itinerary for the day, Google maps is our tour guide once we walk out of the hotel. However, if we decide to stray or get distracted, Google maps is there to save us and get us back on route. Literally it is the difference between a difficult vacation and a painless, and worry free vacation as we are allowed to explore the city (any city) as a local.

Author: Reindeerfan2014
Subject: This is sad
Body:
Google maps is the best app out there for directions. That being said, it’s actually sad that one has to settle for what it offers. I’m one of those people who have to see the exact turns onscreen to have a smooth driving experience.
For example, the map will say turn left but on the visual it points to the right. (I don’t know if I’m the only one who has this issue) but it forces me to rely solely on the voice directions rather than what’s on the screen. This makes me a bit nervous when traveling especially when approaching a turn and I can’t see the street signs anywhere.

Author: Hadijafaria
Subject: Not cool Google. NOT COOL!
Body:
This app has always been an indispensable tool for me. But with the addition of live traffic (in my city) and custom labels recently, it's become an invaluable navigation app. Thank you Google for this app. I generally don't rate and review applications, but I just had to give the new Google Maps the 5 stars it so rightly deserves.

UPDATE:
Took away one star because navigation, location-sharing, and review-writing don’t work in my country. Another star because directions stopped working, too! I hope it’s just a bug and not another one of Google’s arbitrary policies of disabling features for certain countries. Come on Google. DON’T BE EVIL!
BTW, Apple Maps is much more accurate and  detailed than Google Maps now. If Google decides to disable its one saving grace, i.e. directions, altogether, I might as well use the superior Apple Maps.

Author: katochap
Subject: なんだかんだ使ってるけども
Body:
予想所要時間はかなりタイトだと思う。
実際に表示されている時間で走ろうと思うとかなり頑張ってやや飛ばし気味に走らないと実現しないと感じる。
機能としては
経由地を駆使して自分の思い通りのルートを入力して所要時間計算したい。
目的地に対して距離が伸びてもいいから最寄りの高速出口から戻るルートを選択できるようにして欲しい。
高速優先や、有料料金等も細かく条件設定できれば良い。
等々いくつもある。
その辺りは専用のナビの方が優れているが、何といっても常に更新された最新のマップが使えるので旅先で頼りにしてしまう。
但し圏外エリアでは全く役に立たないのと、通信データー量を消費するのでそこが痛い所である。
それら全て実現されると最強に成るだろう。
Translated Body: I think the expected turnaround time is quite tight. I feel I will not realize if I try to run in the actual displayed time and do a lot of hard work and run somewhat skipping. As a function I would like to calculate the required time by inputting my desired route by making use of the waypoint. I'd like you to be able to select the route from the nearest high-speed exit because the distance can be extended relative to the destination. It is only necessary to finely set conditions such as high-speed priority and charged fee. There are many others. In that area, exclusive navigation is superior, but since I always use the latest updated map, I depend on my traveling destination. However, it is totally useless in the out-of-service area, and it consumes communication data volume, so it hurts there. Once they are all realized it will be strongest.

Author: Alexislav
Subject: Плохой навигатор
Body: Навигатор - просто жесть жестокая! Раньше пользовалась Яндекс-навигатором, сейчас это мало реально (на украине яндекс глушат, а с впн навигатор работает некорректно) - приходится искать альтернативу. Гугл-навигатор ею быть никак не может. Скажите, как можно нормально воспринимать подсказку «поверните на юго-восток и следуйте в этом направлении еще 2 км»??? Я так понимаю, мне под рукой еще и компас надо иметь? Или научиться по солнцу ориентироваться, чтоб «юго-восток» сразу и без проблем находить? В общем, если есть необходимость поездки по незнакомому адресу/маршруту, то лучше искать другой навигатор.
Translated Body: Navigator - just hard brutal! Previously, Yandex-navigator used, now it's not really realistic (in Ukraine Yandex dulls, and with VNP the navigator does not work correctly) - we have to look for an alternative. It can not be a Google navigator. Tell me, how can you normally perceive the clue "turn to the southeast and follow in this direction another 2 km" ??? I understand that I still have a compass and I need to have a compass? Or learn by the sun to navigate, so that the "southeast" can be found without any problems at once? In general, if there is a need to travel on an unfamiliar address / route, it is better to look for another navigator.

Author: ShaparenkoStas
Subject: Худший навигатор.
Body:
В Киеве этот навигатор будет предлагать Вам: 
1. Развернуться через 2 сплошные. 
2. Повернуть налево на перекрёстке, где разрешено движение только прямо. 
3. После введения новых правил этот навигатор не знает и не подсказывает где камеры. 
4. Если дорога перекрыта на ремонт (или наоборот, уже открыта) навигатор узнает с опозданием в месяц. 

Ощущение, что обновлением карт никто не занимается.
Translated Body: In Kiev, this navigator will offer you: 1. To unfold through 2 solid ones. 2. Turn left at the intersection, where traffic is allowed only straight. 3. After the introduction of new rules, this navigator does not know and does not tell where the cameras are. 4. If the road is blocked for repair (or vice versa, it is already open), the navigator will find out a delay in a month. The feeling that no one is updating the maps.

Subject: Reliable but loses GPS signal
Body:
- loses GPS signal all the time. Other apps don't -

The number of features is not impressive. The app is purely meant to bring you from A to B. And this is exactly what this app is very good at. The routes proposed are good (no weird routes via small difficult streets) and, very important, the estimated time of arrival is very accurate. Both on the highway and in urban dense areas. The interface is very clean and thus clear. Lane assistance is shown early so that you can prepare well. The database for cameras seems to be a bit outdated. I would love to see a ’via’ option and a way to find e.g. a tank station on the route.

Author: Sam Nome
Subject: In Asien nicht zu gebrauchen
Body: Prinzipiell ist es ja toll, dass man hier auch Offline-Navi mit machen kann. For Asien jedoch fehlen Karten für Kambodscha, Laos und Myanmar. Für Thailand gibt es wohl eine Offline-Karte, jedoch ist hier die Navi mehr als mangelhaft. Bei Autobahnen in Thailand will einen die App zum Beispiel nach rechts führen, was wohl die korrekte Himmelsrichtung wäre, beachtet aber nicht, dass man erst nach links muss um etwas weiter einen U-turn zu machen. Brandgefährlich wäre es hier der App zu vertrauen, denn dann geriete man als Geisterfahrer in den Gegenverkehr. Das passiert mit dieser App ständig. Noch dazu werden die meisten Suchergebnisse in Thai angezeigt. Wer soll das denn lesen können?
Translated Body: In principle, it's great that you can also do offline navigation with. For Asia, however, maps for Cambodia, Laos and Myanmar are missing. For Thailand, there is probably an offline map, but here is the Navi more than faulty. In the case of highways in Thailand, for example, the app wants to lead you to the right, which would be the correct direction, but do not take into account that you have to go to the left to make a U-turn a little further. Fire dangerous it would be here to trust the app, because then you get as a ghost driver in oncoming traffic. This happens with this app constantly. In addition, most search results are displayed in Thai. Who should be able to read that?

Body: Die beste Navigationsapp im Play Store! Karten können für Offline Navigation runtergeladen werden und werden dann nur durch GPS unterstützt - das spart je Menge Strom wenn man kein Ladegerät zur Hand hat.  Die Sprachführung und Kartendarstellung ist super. Der Assistent führt einen sicher und rechtzeitig nicht erst dann wenn man quasi den Lenker rumreißen muss damit man die Kurve noch schafft.  Was ich hervorragend finde, ist der Tempo-Warner. Ist der APP das Tempolimit einer Strecke bekannt und es wird einige Sekunden Überschritten, so gibt die APP eine Akustische Warnung von sich.   Und... Es werden ständig Infos zu Staus aktualisiert. So werden auch neue Staus die bei Suchauftrag unbekannt waren umfahren. Klasse.
Translated Body: The best navigation app in the Play Store! Maps can be downloaded for offline navigation and are then only supported by GPS - this saves a lot of power if you have no charger at hand. The voice guidance and map display is great. The assistant leads a safe and timely not only when you have to pull out the handlebar so that you can still make the curve. What I find excellent is the Tempo Warner. If the APP is aware of the speed limit of a route and it is exceeded a few seconds, the APP beeps. And ... Information about traffic jams is constantly being updated. So also new traffic jams which were unknown with search order are bypassed. Class.

Author: Thomas Vie
Body: Plus: kostenlos professionelle Karten (Abbiege-Information etc.) unlimited zum Download, für Auto-Navigation sind Routen und Ansagen sehr gut, StVO-konforme Navigation.  Bemerkenswert auch, Karten werden in einer Datenbank-Struktur gespeichert. Daher müssen beim Update die Karten nicht komplett neu geladen werden. Hat lange gedauert, aber inzwischen wirklich ausgereift und stabil. Minus: Für Fahrrad oder Fußgänger wegen fehlenden Karten-Details nur im Notfall brauchbar.  Eigentlich selbstverständliche Funktionen wie "reisen über" oder gar über mehrere Stationen fehlen. Fazit: fürs Auto in DE konkurrenzlos gut in der Kategorie "für umsonst" da bei hiesigen Tarifen Online-Navis kaum in Frage kommen. NACHTRAG: hat mich inzwischen zu oft irgendwo auf dem Dorf völlig im Stich gelassen oder in Großstädten auf absurde Routen geschickt. Behalte die App nur noch als Backup -- die herausragend gute Sprachansage wird mir allerdings fehlen.
Translated Body: Plus: free professional maps (turn-off information, etc.) unlimited for download, for car navigation routes and announcements are very good, StVO-compliant navigation. Remarkably, maps are stored in a database structure. Therefore, the cards do not have to be completely reloaded during the update. Has taken a long time, but now really mature and stable. Minus: For bicycle or pedestrian due to missing map details only in case of emergency. Actually self-evident functions such as "traveling over" or even missing over several stations. Conclusion: For the car in Germany unrivaled good in the category "for free" because at local rates online Navis hardly come into question. ADDENDUM: In the meantime, I have too often deserted myself somewhere in the village or sent on absurd routes in big cities. Keep the app only as a backup - but I will miss the excellent voice response.

Author: josh miller
Body: This app is AWFUL!!! Used it for years but it doesn't predict traffic well and takes me to the wrong place sometimes. For example: went on a trip last week and the GPS redirected me due to 20 mins of traffic but did not account for the traffic along the new route which was over 2.5 hours. Sent me into 2.5 hours of traffic to avoid the 20 min of traffic along original route. TERRIBLE. I downloaded Waze during the 2.5 hours of traffic and it immediately told me there was a major accident. Google maps still to this day never explained why I was sitting in that traffic, no notice whatsoever of new traffic. Trust me Waze is 1000x better.

Author: Ralf S.

Navigation sollte ein eigenes Modul sein, um die eigentliche Kernanwendung schlanker zu halten. Die Navigation ist brauchbar (kein Navi ist perfekt) und die Sprachsteuerung im Auto sehr hilfreich! Mir fehlt nur noch die Anzeige der vorherrschenden Geschwindigkeitsbeschränkungen, um die anderen on Board Naviprogramme nur noch in Funklöchern anwerfen zu müssen.

Author: Teddy Wahyudi
Body: Saya suka sekali aplikasi ini  Bisa membantu saya untuk berpergian jauh dan bisa lihat foto" nya (Pertahan kan dan tingkat kan lagi aplikasi nya)

С каждым обновлением приложение тупит всё сильнее и сильнее, после последнего обновления приложения стало открываться почти 2 минуты, сделать какое-нибудь действие, например, сдвинуть карту - 12 секунд. Ужас. Недавно пользовался стареньким теефоном, там стоял ГуглМэп версия 2013-го года, КАРТЫ ЛЕТАЮТ, любое действие происходило мгновенного. И что сейчас?! Не понимаю народ, который маниакально гонится за этими идиотскими обновлениями. На нормальном железе, качественное приложение будет работать десятилетиями без всяких обновлений. Я вот юзаю МС ОФИС 2003-го года, один и тотже устанавливаю на все компы  15 лет уже и никаких обновлений, боже упаси. Вас кормят этой шнягой, а вы как хомячки хаваете и просите ещё, долбоебизм...

Body: App USED to be awesome. NOW THIS APP SUCKS. While driving it will say "in a quarter mile turn right", and not tell you the name of the road, or street . So then I need to take my eyes off of the road, and look at the screen to see where I should be turning.   Then I say, ok Google, what is my next turn, or what is the name of the street that I will be turning on,, and it says, "I don't know how to help you with that", and then says,. "if you need help, turn on the microphone and ask for help" Well I did that, and again it says it doesn't know how to help me with that. GOOGLE,. HOW CAN. THAT BE? IT USED TO WORK BRILLIANTLY, AND NOW IT IS UTTER RUBISH. SHAME ON GOOGLE AND ITS ENGINEERS,. OWNERS, DEVELOPERS, ANYONE ELSE ASSOCIATED WITH THIS APP. WHY IS IT NOW ACCEPTABLE TO RELEASE A PRODUCT THAT IS SUBSTANDARD AND HAS DEGRESSED IN QUALITY AND FUNCTIONALITY ???? WHY GOOGLE???  AND WHY DO. YOU. FOLKS INSULATE YOURSELVES FROM THE FEEDBACK OF YOUR CUSTOMERS? AND OFFER ZERO CUSTOMER SERVICE???

Body: Necesito ver el puntero del vehículo mientras me muevo como era antes con el triángulo que va hacia el frente y gira cuando yo giro moviendo el mapa de manera que siempre vayamos hacia el frente.  Tuve que desinstalar las actualizaciones porque ahora en vez de un triangulo veo un circulo que hace referencia a mi ubicación y no se mueve conmigo hacia el frente, sino que el mapa se queda fijo y se mueve el punto en el mapa y me marea y me hace confundir hacia donde voy y hacia donde doblar! Y cuando acomodo el mapa para "ir al frente" con el puntero el mapa se queda en el lugar y el puntero se va solo. Pongo "centrar" y volvemos a lo mismo, veo el mapa desde arriba yendo para cualquier lado y no distingo bien hacia donde voy o donde tengo que doblar.
Pô o que aconteceu??um baita aplicativo muito eficiente!!Virar nisso!!

Author: Persa Lucian
Body: As vrea sa stiu care sunt probleme celor care nu le merge. Sa postam ca  "nu merge", "sunteti de rahat", etc.nu ajuta. Bine ca sunteti voi destepti si va pricepeti la programare. Sa spunem care sunt problemele reale. Sa spunem ce am dori (oricum, unde sunt mai multi de doi, nu poti multumi pe toata lumea). Sa injuram este cel simplu mod de exprimare, mai ales daca esti in spatele unui monitor (de aia s-au inventat retelele sociale). Iar in cazul unora (celor mai multi), limba romana in exprimare (no comment) este limba straina. Din unele comentarii nu poti sa iti dai seama ce vor de fapt. Daca tot te bagi in seama, spune clar, cu subiect si predicat care e problema. Si inca un sfat:  decat sa areti ca un cretin, mai bine taci si sa fii luat de prost.
Translated Body: I'd like to know what's wrong with those who do not. Let's post it "does not work", "you're shit," etc. do not help. Good that you are smart and you will be able to understand the programming. Let's say what the real problems are. Let's say what we want (anyway, where there are more than two, you can not thank everyone). Letting us lecture is the simple way of expressing, especially if you are behind a monitor (that's why social networks were invented). And in the case of some (most), the Romanian language in expression (no comment) is foreign language. From some reviews you can not figure out what they really want. If you keep on track, say clearly, with subject and preached what the problem is. And another tip: than to look like a shit, better shut up and get stupid.

Author: Roman Grenda
Body: Карты не плохие, но есть недостатки, которые пора бы уже было исправить к 2018 году. Некоторые недочёты просто убивают и льшь говорят о нежелании гугл делать какие-либо подвижки в корректировке программы. Например, сделали возможность офф-лайн карт, это хорошо. Но почему не дать возможность загрузки карты отдельных городов или регионов как у конкурентов? Не всегда загружаемая область посещаемого регилна влазит в предложенный Гуглом квадрат для офф-лайн карт, а интернетом в роуминге не всегда пользуюсь. И сделайте что-нибудь с масштабированием: силуэты зданий появляются при очень сильном приближении, но в таком случае информативность карты падает, так как перестает быть видно здания вокруг (так по крайней мере на телефоне выглядит, может на планшете лучше, но проверить нет возможности, так как планшет откинул коньки). А в больших городах, где высота зданий превышает 9 этажей, строения будто бы "влетают" в экран.
Translated Body: The cards are not bad, but there are drawbacks, which it would be time to fix by 2018. Some shortcomings are just killing and talking about the unwillingness of Google to make any progress in adjusting the program. For example, made the possibility of off-line cards, it's good. But why not give the possibility of loading maps of individual cities or regions as competitors? The not always downloadable area of ​​the visited region is in the square offered by Google for off-line maps, and I do not always use the Internet when roaming. And do something with the scaling: the silhouettes of the buildings appear with a very strong approximation, but in this case the informativity of the map falls, as the buildings around are no longer visible (at least on the phone it looks, maybe on the tablet is better, as the tablet has thrown off the skates). And in large cities, where the height of buildings exceeds 9 floors, the structures seem to "fly into" the screen.

Author: A Google User
Body: This is quite honestly a life changing app. Using these maps for directions and trip planning is incredibly easy and very helpful. I do have a suggestion. The route planner algorithm needs updating. It seems that the route loves to put you on an interstate for a trip even if it saves 1 minute, compared to a 'no interstate' route. This should not be the default as many times interstates are crowded and traffic always ends up being worse than initially forecasted - thus a longer trip. There are usually a multitude of more efficient routes, Google Maps needs to get away from focusing solely on the 'How long it takes to get from point A to point B' and think about efficiency instead.

App: Waze - GPS, Maps, Traffic Alerts & Live Navigation
Author: Vladimir Ballesteros-Moreno
Body: It's ok but I've been using waze to navigate in Los Angeles and it's provides wrong directions when the destination is about to be approached. Waze miscalculated the destination entered and as a result do not take you to the street registered. Waze ended up sending you into alleys, tunnels in DTLA, a side street or to the street/roads behind the house or buildings. Also waze try to send you into the middle of the block when there is not streets and if you are going to any beach city waze set up your destination to go into water. You must know the area to avoid this hassle or recheck your route when you can. Do not rely 100% on this app to navigate in Los Angeles and use your city knowledge too

App: Waze - GPS, Maps, Traffic Alerts & Live Navigation
Author: William Voss
Body: This app pairs very well with a radar detector. Radar detectors are great for defense against police radar detectors, however police are using laser more and more often which a radar detector will not protect you against. However since police can only use a laser gun while stopped it is common that they are reported on waze which helps tremendously since laser jamming systems cost a ton of money.

App: Waze - GPS, Maps, Traffic Alerts & Live Navigation
Author: gareth cocklin
Body: Been using this app for a few years and it's great.  I did my motorcycle everyday to and from work and have this in my ear. I love the police / speed camera warnings, but most of all I love the hazard warnings and the other Waze users that report them, there have been 2 instances within the last 6 months of hazards reported in the road on the freeway and if I'd have not known, I'd have not backed off the throttle and opened a bigger gap on the cars infront, this app literally has saved my life or at least prevented me having a nasty accedent. THANK YOU.  On a negative or a improvement . As you can tell I believe this app saaves my life, but it could do with a motor cycle mode, as when I put phone in pocket, sometimes Waze shuts, or if I take to long putting g my gear on seems to pause. Maybe a nose every 2 or three mins to let me know she's still watching out for me. Please have a motorcycle mode as that would make perfect. Thanks again. And everyone should use it.

Author: Eric Caldwell
Body: ********** SUGGESTIONS ********** Here are some suggestions to make this app even better than it already is:  DELETE REPORTS AND EDIT Ability to delete reports made by you (such as accidental reports) And ability to edit reports that you have made  REMOVE OR REDUCE ROAD CLOSURE REPORT RESTRICTIONS AND ADD MORE FEATURES Since we sometimes know that there is or is going to be a road closure, please give us the ability to mark that location without having to drive there. Also, please give us the ability to set a specific start date and time and end date and time for the road closure.  INSTANT REPORTS Macros... the ability to place single-tap buttons on the screen to instantly report something that you have previously typed out.      #suggestion #suggestions #recommendation #recommendations #improvement #improvements #feedback #idea #ideas      Edit Log:    Original  2018-01-19-0045-JAN-FRI-EST  Edit 1 (Formatting Corrections) 2018-01-19-0010-JAN-FRI-EST

Author: Carlos Eduardo Delgado Correa
Body: Ultimamente esta muy mal, avisa tardíamente, a cada momento cambia de ruta como si se perdiera el gps, se mantiene recalculando ruta sin sentido de ubicacion, por ejemplo en una parada de semaforo recalcula la ruta y envia por una que no tiene nada que ver con el destino, se demora mucho en iniciar la ruta correcta, en las noches cuando no hay congestion vehicular envia por rutas largas e inseguras, cuando el destino es mas cerca y se podria evitar dar vueltas inecesarias, utilizo dentro de la configuracion no tomar caminos destapados y me envia por sitios totalmente destapados no aptos para automoviles, se presentan nomenclaturas con letras a, b, c, d... y se enrreda en estas situaciones; desde enero de 2018 esta totalmente en caos, tanto que estoy pensando en desinstalar y tomar otra opcion. Gracias.

Si no fuese por este "gran detalle" le pondría 5 estrellas Si me vuelve a pasar lo mismo lo elimino definitivamente y busco otra app que haga lo mismo

Author: Ian Blaiklock
Body: Like the layout, warning of cameras, police etc. Don't like difficulty in seeing alternative routes. Handled much better in Google maps. Want to see on the map the alternative route and additional time or time saving whilst driving and be able to select it. Also in the overview, alternative routes should be seen and selectable. In waze, too many clicks to see alternates and to change settings between with tolls and without tolls.

App Name: Waze - GPS, Maps, Traffic Alerts & Live Navigation
App: Waze - GPS, Maps, Traffic Alerts & Live Navigation
Author: Glenn Latch
Body: Very heavy battery drain. My phone discharges whilst charging and using Waze. When using Google Maps, my phone charges, so it's obvious Waze sucks up juice.  The interface is tiny, so updating road hazards, etc.os difficult and unsafe.  Waze randomly directs me off the most direct route, often with a longer projected travel time.  Apart from the numerously broken bits, Waze has great potential. I think Google should just bite the bullet and migrate all the good stuff across to Maps.

Body: In het begin was het even wennen. Navigeerde voorheen veel met HERE (offline) en daarna met een data-abonnement met Google Maps (online). Ook Flitsmeister draaide op de achtergrond voor de 'flitsers' ed. Ik gebruik nu alleen maar Waze en vind het een top app. Werkelijk alles in één en nog veel beter! Wel belangrijk is dat een 'Wazer' zelf ook bijdraagt middels input tav verkeers situaties, mobiele controles etc. Het is een vorm sociale community. Ik zeg doen!

Body: Aplikasi waze: GPS Navigation, maps & rambu lalu lintas. Sistem kerja aplikasi maps offline yang relatif sama dengan aplikasi sebelumnya. Tapi ada beberapa keunggulan waze diantaranya pengemudi bakalan mendapat peringatan rambu lalu lintas disekitar, batas kecepatan, pengisian bahan bakar, bahkan area parkir. Sementara bagi pejalan kaki, waze akan memberikan referensi tempat wisata terdekat, hotel restoran dan sebagainya lengkap hanya di waze, terbukti di google play store waze sudah di unduh lebih dari 100 juta pengguna android. Maestro Frenlin
Translated Body: Application waze: GPS Navigation, maps & traffic signs. Offline maps application working system that is relatively the same as the previous application. But there are some advantages waze among drivers will get warning signs of traffic around, speed limits, refueling, even parking areas. As for pedestrians, waze will provide references to nearby attractions, hotel restaurants and so forth complete only in waze, proved in google play store waze has been downloaded more than 100 million android users. Maestro Frenlin

Author: Jason Price
Body: This app puts the cream in your cupcake. Like super deep, all up in there. So many of drivings nooks and crannys get slathered with the hot dripping features of Wazes' frosting. Its like a coat of white chocolate drizzled all over you experience and it just keeps the hot drizzle coming the harder and deeper you push forward on your journey. If your pressing up on a couple huge mounds or pounding your way fast & steady into the bush while your getting wet and juiced from rain. This app gives you just what you need... Body: Как я понял, это навигатор для Европы, США, ещё чего-то. Но только не для России. Ну, может ещё в Москве-Питере сгодится, не проверял. Я живу в Казани, город миллионик. Моего дома 92-года года постройки нет. Нет целых кварталов. Причем мой район массово застраивался в 80-90-ых. А наших домов нет. Торговые центры есть зато, почти все. Зачем тогда этот навигатор  таким как я? С такими картами в России ловить ему нечего, и жители России скачав его, просто потеряют время.
Translated Body: As I understand it, it's a navigator for Europe, the United States, something else. But not for Russia. Well, maybe even in Moscow-Peter fit, did not check. I live in Kazan, a city of million. My house is not built in 1992. There are no whole blocks. And my area was massively built up in the 80-90's. And our houses do not. Shopping centers are there, almost everything. Why then is this navigator like me? With such cards in Russia, he has nothing to catch, and the inhabitants of Russia downloading it will simply lose time.

Author: Andrew Kalinin
Body: Jerky scrolling on android even on powerful smartphones.  Your position jump constantly if there are small streets close to you.  Annoying reminder to rate the app whilst it had been already rated.   There is quite tricky way to add a location picked up from map to favourites.  App did not started averagely once a half year even after phone restart. Reinstall helped.  For what reason waze asks permission to access my contact when I choose to login with phone number? In case of Deny just do not proceed further.   Waze made a great thing: event reporting. But they seem to stop on it and do not improve other things essential to navigation app.

Es por eso que solo les doy 4 estrellas. Les propongo que todos sus paquetes de voz los tengan disponibles, incluso si tuvieran costo estoy seguro que todos comprariamos nuestro favorito.
Translated Body: Waze is a great browser, and something that makes it stand out is the ability to configure voice packages, have had great success in Latin audios but unfortunately are only available for some time. That's why I only give them 4 stars. I propose that all your voice packages have them available, even if they had cost I'm sure we would all buy our favorite.

Author: Keith Botelho
Body: I looked at this app a few days ago and the rating was down to 3.9, now it is at 4.6 with hundreds if not thousands of accounts giving 5 stars. Seems very suspect. This app has went down hill and now it seems as though they are trying to hide it. Sad... ____________________________________  I have been using this app for awhile now and love it. Well, until this new release.    1. There used to be a way to remove addresses from your favorites now I can't seem to find that button. 2. It has frozen on me while driving a couple of times. 3. Reporting events while using a tablet is damn near impossible because the buttons are so far apart. 4. Stopping navigation is hidden. 5. And there is no way to turn off the reporting of "pot holes" . I live in New England they are everywhere because of the salt used on the roads in the winter.  Great app just need to make some tweaks....

Author: vovgam
Subject: Fix it! It’s not safe to use this app
Body: Please, fix the issue with voice directions.. while on wifi voices appear to be working, but as soon as I get in my car while on cellular I get an error “error downloading voice pack. Try again later”. Why??? I’ve already downloaded it while on wifi. Then my whole trip I get no voice directions which make me check my phone all the time. I get distracted because of it. FIX IT or i’ll delete it.

Author: The Last Man 56
Subject: can't use till audio bug is fixed
Body: Multitasking with Waze causes audio to cut out. Will use another nav app until it's fixed.

Author: Dadou1132
Subject: Super mais...
Body:
Excellente appli à laquelle il ne manque qu'une chose: la fonctionnalité couplée avec Apple CarPlay. 
Peut-on espérer voir cela prochainement pour 2018 ??
Translated Body: Great app that lacks one thing: the functionality coupled with Apple CarPlay. Can we hope to see this soon for 2018 ??

Author: Triannap
Subject: Terrible
Body: Waze used to be the best GPS app.  Not sure what happened, but over the past couple of years I have had several instances where it rerouted me along the same route multiple times before moving me forward on my route. I also have had several occasions where the app has a energy delay updating my current location and gives me incorrect directions or in efficient directions from a point where I was located five minutes before. It is causing me to be late for very important meetings.

Author: ramalski
Subject: Missing Live Traffic Bar
Body:
This app really needs a live traffic bar that is always visible as in its current form you can’t see any upcoming traffic/accidents without having to zoom really far out and nearly crash yourself!!!

It’s for this reason I keep deleting the app and going back to Tomtom. Then 3 months later I reinstall to see if it’s now available but it’s not so I delete again and then repeat 3 months later.

Absence of this very disappointing given the amount of people who have requested this functionality. 

Take a look at tomtom go's bar on the right hand side. This is what Waze needs !

Also give us the settings to receive audible speed camera alerts regardless of if we are below or above the speed limit!

Author: Samylmy
Subject: Esta super!!
Body: Super util y me quita de todo el tráfico!!
Translated Body: Super useful and I removed all traffic!

Author: Amrodsr1
Subject: Waze
Body: Waze is a great app which leads you with road reports and conditions reported by fellow wagers.

Author: Lcoarm
Subject: Ottimo navigare
Body:
È il navigatore che uso costantemente tutti i giorni. Grafica ottima, voce della navigatrice buona, affidabile sui limiti ed ha gli autovelox.
L’unico difetto che la voce della navigatrice ti dice la presenza degli autovelox solo se si supera i limiti, a me sarebbe piaciuto lo dicesse sempre.
Risulta possibile segnalare agli altri utenti la presenza di lavoro in corso, code, autovelox mobili o altri ostacoli.
Veramente ottimo!
Translated Body: It is the navigator that I use constantly every day. Excellent graphics, the navigator's voice is good, reliable on the limits and has speed cameras. The only flaw that the voice of the navigator tells you the presence of speed cameras only if you exceed the limits, I would have liked to say it always. It is possible to report to other users the presence of work in progress, queues, mobile safety cameras or other obstacles. Really great!

Author: TheRother7
Subject: Special kind of stupid
Body: It takes a very special kind of stupid to implement a toggle like “control Waze from car unit” and design it to not function.  I want to be able to plug my phone into my USB port and not have it default to my stereo to control it.  Once this happens, I need to disconnect the app and it then only appears on half of my phone screen.  Congratulations of having some special programmers and ruining a great app!!

Author: Severine casimir
Subject: Précision
Body:
Il manque des précisions sur la bande de navigation quand il y a un souci... souvent il faut attendre d être sur le problème pour être averti !!
Autrement l application est top 😆
Merci 
Severine.
Translated Body: It lacks details on the navigation band when there is a problem ... often we must wait to be on the problem to be notified! Otherwise the application is top 😆 Thank you Severine.

Author: ShoelessScott
Subject: Still Absolute Necessity!
Body:
I plan all driving through Waze down to the minute.  Saves me run-ins with the police and reroutes me through traffic effectively and consistently. 
Must have!

Update (01/2018): The only time I have a problem is when I think I’m smarter than Waze and ignore it when it says to detour.  I was driving to San Antonio from North Texas and Waze told me to exit the freeway and take a 20 minutes detour in the middle of nowhere. I knew the traffic jam 10 miles ahead couldn’t be that bad, and if it was, I’d take another exit and go around it. Nope. 65 minutes sitting completely still with concrete construction barriers on either side of me. 
Just follow the Wade’s suggested detour.

Author: Hans Vakantie
Subject: Perfect
Body: Veel beter dan mijn Tom Tom live, en zeker veel goedkoper.!
Translated Body: Much better than my Tom Tom live, and certainly much cheaper!

Author: Jtizjr
Subject: AWESOMENESS
Body: No doubt the best navigation app!

Author: Abang Long Fadil
Subject: Was Waze, Is Google Maps
Body: Waze is reliable no more. Before it was my favorite Navigation apps as everything was extremely fast and accurate. Now to launch takes time, less accuracy, longer route, busier route and also directions are extremely confusing especially on many exits at intersection.

Author: 123whoCares
Subject: Love it
Body: Just wish that I had more control over my route, like there is a highway that I want to avoid and because it is the most direct route, it sends me that way.  No other option.  I just have to drive the route I want to go and hope when I get there that traffic isn’t crazy.  Also the physical addresses aren’t as accurate as Google Maps.  Gets you close, but Google gets you closer.

Author: misschickpea
Subject: Great Navigation but lately has PROBLEMS
Body: Absolutely love the way Waze gets me around town, HOWEVER, it has not been functioning up to par these last few weeks. UNDERESTIMATES ARRIVAL TIME when it used to be precise. DOES NOT ALERT “Time to Leave” even tho notifications and location services are ON. FORGETS that I requested navigation and STOPS GUIDING when I lock my phone... What’s going on, Waze?! I have a new and fully-functional phone so we can’t blame the device. App experience hasn’t been what it used to. Update please :(

Author: TOTAL WHITE
Subject: Problemi con GPS
Body:
Ogni 2x3 problemi con il GPS!!!!! 
Mentre con altri navigatori problemi zero!!!
Translated Body: Every 2x3 problems with GPS !!!!! While with other browsers problems zero !!!

Author: trainstationblues
Subject: Inefficient Routing
Body: This app took me through the circuitous, congested route that took me about 10 minutes longer than Google Maps. While stuck in traffic, I pulled up Google Maps, which provided me an alternate route with a short ETA. I've confirmed several times that Waze provides the slower routes of the 2 apps, and has ads to boot.

Author: JOkee1234
Subject: Great app...  WHEN IT WORKS!
Body:
Been user for a couple of years, but for last week or two very time I try to use this for my morning commute I get a “routing server error” and it doesn’t give me directions. 

Great when it works but useless to me now.

Author: Alessio italy
Subject: Pessimo
Body: Da quando la Apple ha imposto a tutte le app che usano il GPS di dare agli utenti la possibilità di disattivarlo quando “non in uso”, Waze non funziona più, o meglio, è lento e riceve il segnale GPS peggio di qualsiasi altro navigatore nello store. Waze, e molte altre app, hanno interesse a raccogliere i dati di posizione degli utenti per tanti motivi. Nel mondo dell’Internet of Things, tanti più sono i dati raccolti, tanto maggiori le possibilità di sfruttarli a fini economici. Che l’app sia “gratuita” è mera illusione, tanto più ora che è stata acquisita dalla Google. La Apple, giustamente, ha impedito a Waze di avere sempre attivo la localizzazione (GPS su “sempre”) poiché in tal modo consuma la batteria oltre ogni tollerabilità, anche quando non usato. Risultato? Alla Google la mossa di Apple non deve essere piaciuta, o forse sta spingendo verso Google Maps. Consiglio? Spendete due lire e compratevi un navigatore che funziona anche offline.
Translated Body: Since Apple has imposed on all the apps that use the GPS to give users the ability to disable it when "not in use", Waze no longer works, or rather, it is slow and receives the GPS signal worse than any other navigator in the store. Waze, and many other apps, are interested in collecting user location data for many reasons. In the world of the Internet of Things, the more data are collected, the greater the chances of exploiting them for economic purposes. That the app is "free" is a mere illusion, especially now that it has been acquired by Google. Apple, rightly, has prevented Waze from always having the location active (GPS on "always") because in this way consumes the battery beyond all tolerability, even when not used. Result? At Google the Apple move should not be liked, or maybe it's pushing towards Google Maps. Council? Spend two liras and buy a browser that also works offline.

Author: lba_92
Subject: Pb de déconnexion / reboot avec CarPlay actif
Body:
Bonjour,
Utilisateur de l’Iphone X, je constate lorsque je suis en mode GPS Waze actif et que je souhaite émettre un appel via l’appli Contact iOS, à l’issu de l’appel et lorsque je revient sur l’app Waze, mon itinéraire est arrêté. Je suis obligé de relancé une demande d’itinéraire.

D’autre part, lorsque je suis en mode CarPlay, l’utilisation de Waze associé à l’irisation de l’app Contact lors de l’émission d’un appel entraîne un reboot de l’iPhone X et une perte de navigation.

Merci pour vos correctifs !
Translated Subject: Pb of disconnection / reboot with active CarPlay
Translated Body: Hello, Iphone X user, I notice when I am in Waze GPS mode and I want to make a call via the iOS Contact App, at the end of the call and when I return to the Waze app , my route is stopped. I am obliged to relaunch a route request. On the other hand, when I'm in CarPlay mode, the use of Waze associated with the iridescence of the Contact app when making a call results in a reboot of the iPhone X and a loss of navigation. Thank you for your corrections!

Subject: Tenha sempre os melhores caminhos!

For the Dev:

- when I use my iPhone X and I plug the device at my infotainment system, at my Civic Honda, using the HDMI cable, my iPhone X screen freezes. I can see the Waze map at my infotainment, but I can’t trace routes or do anything at my iPhone, even it shows a disconnect button on the screen. This feature will be awesome when it starts  working 100%.
Translated Body: Krikaoli recommends! After the wheel, this was one of the best inventions of mankind. This application is perfect for choosing the least time-consuming way! No lawyer will ever lose time, and boyfriend will always be able to tell exactly how long she will be at her girlfriend's house. The app lays out the best route, the driver will never have surprises in traffic. For the Dev: - when I use my iPhone X and I plug the device at my infotainment system, at my Civic Honda, using the HDMI cable, my iPhone X screen freezes. I can see the Waze map at my infotainment, but I can not trace routes from anything at my iPhone, even it shows a disconnect button on the screen. This feature will be awesome when it starts working 100%.

Subject: 中国区地图数据严重缺失
Body:

2、不能提供离线下载地图数据，高昂的流量让人承受不起，限制了人群的使用频率！
3、道路错误多
改进意见：
1、使用谷歌地图数据或者加入众包模式。
2、提供区域离线地图数据下载。
Translated Subject: Map data in China is a serious lack of
Translated Body: To mention a few deficiencies and the need to improve the place: 1, China's lack of serious map data, resulting in a lot of people do not want to use! 2, can not provide offline download map data, high traffic can not afford to limit the frequency of use of the crowd! 3, improve the views of many road mistakes: 1, the use of Google Maps data or join crowdsourcing mode. 2, to provide regional offline map data download.

Author: MacSnout
Subject: De beste navigatie tot heden
Body:
Snel, actueel en overzichtelijk. 
Op basis van actuele (Waze) verkeersinfo wordt een omleiding automatisch en snel in je route doorgevoerd. Al veel files hierdoor omzeild. 

De hoge actualiteit van de Waze-verkeersinfo wordt gerealiseerd door een eenvoudig te bedienen meldsysteem voor verkeersincidenten en gestimuleerd door dankbare feedback van andere Waze gebruikers op dat traject. 

Kan gewoonweg niet beter !
Translated Body: Fast, up-to-date and clear. Based on current (Waze) traffic information, a diversion is automatically and quickly implemented in your route. This has already circumvented many files. The high news of the Waze traffic information is realized by an easy-to-use traffic incident reporting system and stimulated by grateful feedback from other Waze users on that route. Simply can not be better!

Translated Body: Simply the best, it is updated continuously by the users, unfortunately it needs internet all the time and here in Brazil unfortunately our internet does not catch on all the highways and in many cities, it would be even better if we had the option to edit the configurations of our vehicles this would be very useful to the professional drivers and drivers who do not know all the places where they are indicated to pass and thus would also avoid any inconvenience if we had the restrictions of highways and heights of viaducts and walkways to avoid traffic accidents and much more 👏🏻

Author: IphoneLoverWoo
Subject: Highly disappointed
Body:
EDIT Jan 2018: 3 stars
One of the updates in the past 3-5 months has really negatively impacted performance. Firstly, now it takes much too long to launch.

Secondly, now if I program it when at a standstill (the SAFE way), half the time it doesn't seem to know which way I'm facing. So for example, I get started and turn left, and then it swivels all around and I discover I should have turned right, and now I'm heading the wrong way, because it can't tell how I'm holding the phone. This can be a real problem to remedy in some circumstances.

(Orig review, 5 stars). This is now my exclusive mapping app. It has real time reports of traffic conditions that are provided by other Wazers, so it always chooses the best route. For example, most of the time I take the same way to work, but every now and then it sends me a different way. Since my husband and I both have it, I love the ETA function as well. Also, if you drive into an area without cell service, it can still continue to guide you.

Author: GaryQual
Subject: Disappointing usability, data/power consumption
Body:
I was shocked at basic usability missteps. At about the one mile mark, it said something like "in one mile, take the exit", without telling us which exit, since of course there are at least two at the exchange.  Fortunately, we knew where we were going, as this was just a test, but it's insane to warn about an exit without at least an exit number or direction. 

Then, with a simple test at home, I realized the bloody app kept using location, and hence battery, even when I'm not using it for directions and not running it.  Neither Apple maps nor google maps does that. That's either stupid programming or some selfish reason.  But I keep my costs down and maximize battery power by never using data unexpectedly. Worse, there's no obvious way to tell it to stop using location. I had to force shut the app the first few times. Eventually I found it, but it's stupid. When permissions are set to only when running, and I'm not getting directions, it's supposed to stop use location to respect the privacy settings.

Author: Sxxxx Wxxxx
Subject: Long overdue fixes...
Body:
Update: wondering why the navigation window won't remain in the view parameters we choose, and yet once we've taken the time to set it up, the data bar reverts to "overview" or " recenter" only options, and eventually it will automatically force change to whatever view it decides we want. Senseless. 

So, as much as I appreciate the functionality of your app, I find the same miserable and unresolved mistakes to be frustrating and disappointing all at the same time. I know I'm not the only one asking for and app-support-logging fixes of; 1) less cartoonishly rendered, better labeled map names on streets and boulevards (for years now), 2) for you to fix the glitch with Favorites, where the order, post-edit, slowly becomes randomized and self-rearranges (and not based on any actual usage metrics, and for years now), 3) how about actual destination addresses upon arrival in the arrival pop-up?, 4) a dotted instead of solid purple route highlight so we can distinguish traffic/the underlying flow color designations (for years now), 5) poor search function as company name + actual street address – even coming from a Google Search (!), and etc, but that's good for now... Thx

Author: JLBiv
Subject: Critically Flawed - inaccurate position indication
Body:
When a destination is selected and Waze is providing route guidance, the on-screen vehicle position indicator lags the real world position of your vehicle. Meaning that by the time Waze shows you at your turn, you’ve missed it. Worse, in this latest version, the lag is inconsistent, so you can’t even make allowance for it.

Not a huge deal on the highway where exits are far enough apart to avoid any confusion, but it renders the app useless for actual guidance in town.

If you know where you’re going, then Waze can still help by keeping you informed about traffic and road conditions. But if you need guidance and are in town, beware.

Author: M4GoD
Subject: Dégradation
Body: Depuis plusieurs mise à jour je constate, sans réelle explication qu’il y a une perte de qualité dans le guidage. Parfois lent au point de louper une intersection, ou approximatif dans l’explication. Le démarrage est systématiquement mal orienté. Et enfin, le choix du parcours est parfois hallucinant ! Au point de mettre en danger... pourtant l’option utiliser les chemins ou intersection dangereuse n’est pas activée. Seul la communauté et l’info trafic est fiable et me motive à l’utiliser encore.
Translated Body: Since several update I note, without real explanation that there is a loss of quality in the guidance. Sometimes slow to the point of missing an intersection, or approximate in the explanation. Startup is systematically misguided. And finally, the choice of the course is sometimes amazing! To the point of endangering ... yet the option to use paths or dangerous intersection is not activated. Only the community and traffic info is reliable and motivates me to use it again.

Subject: Delays
Body:
Waze has unfortunately joined other sat nav apps (most noticeable being tomtom) by having your location on the screen lagging behind where you actually are. Ergo, missed turns as I’ve passed it, or directly at the turn, by the time Waze considers verbally and on screen that I’m am still approaching said turn. 

Waze developers: simple preventative solution: update the software then use it to drive home. Release it whence you are happy with your efforts. Rocket science?

Thank you for reading.

Yes, my iPhone software is up to date, phone powered off/on and app restarted 100x in attempt to fix the problem.

Author: iSeptimus
Subject: Was good once
Body: Annoying ads that don’t go, slow response, rerouting onto longer journeys to save mere seconds. No CarPlay support. It’s now been properly “Googled” and just another Ad gateway.

Author: Sebby561
Subject: Uber and Lyft
Body: I’ve been using Waze for both apps and Waze is right 10% of the time . It’s taking me on unnecessary turns and roads . I wish Lyft and Uber would dump this app

Author: Rwidtowowiw
Subject: Au top mais?
Body: Bonjour je rencontre un problème avec la carte de navigation qui ne se positionne plus face route! Pas très clair mais en gros l indication de tranjet n est plus en plein écran je vois l ensemble du trajet et du coup difficile de se baser à la flèche d aide.
Translated Body: Hello I am having a problem with the navigation map which is no longer positioned facing road! Not very clear but basically the indication of tranjet is no longer full screen I see the whole path and difficult to hit the arrow help.

Author: ChicagoDave312
Subject: Can we get rid of the pulsing search icon?
Body: I used to keep Waze on for general traffic information even when I wasn't navigating somewhere. But now with the big blinking search icon it's way too distracting. Please make it stop or at least make it optional.

Author: KoDiaK8531
Subject: Great APP
Body:
I think this app is by far one of the best gps app’s out there. I work in a very heavy populated area and this app will tell you in a split second if there is a faster route. The safety features help by letting you know if cars are on the side of the road. I really like being able to chat with people and see what is wrong if your stuck in traffic because of a wreck or something. 

Flaws that I see: Sometimes when your driving and it says there is a wreck it not there.

Author: Rnsin
Subject: Bug
Body: Depuis la dernière mise à jour, impossible d’utiliser Waze. Il n’y a plus aucune route visible sur l’écran. Quand bien même on puisse rentrer une adresse, ensuite, l’écran est gris. Les instructions apparaissent uniquement mais plus de carte.
Translated Body: Since the last update, you can not use Waze. There is no visible route on the screen. Even if we can enter an address, then the screen is gray. The instructions appear only but no map.

Author: Kimmie1139
Subject: Good up to date traffic/gps app
Body:
I love mostly every feature of this app, except the location preference needs an option of knowing my location "while using google" the app. I do not like apps ALWAYS using my location.. and always using my battery!
Other complaint is I wish waze would notify me there has been reports of congested traffic ahead (without a wreck being reported) and let me know that of a possible different route! I use this app because I work downtown in my area and I prefer not to be stuck on the interstate due to merging delays and construction delays when there has already been reports of slow traffic. 

Also please make an Apple Watch compatible app!!

Author: CaptJamesKid
Subject: When it works it’s good, but the app needs serious help.
Body: I used to use Waze religiously, and then randomly half my points disappeared.  It took 4 months to get a response from Waze and their answer was basically to remove my usage history because of their own app’s issues.  Google Maps is much more trustworthy.

Author: Reload_Spain
Subject: Sin soporte Galileo
Body: Sin soporte de la constelación Galileo.
Translated Body: Without support of the Galileo constellation.

Author: Harry the forgetter
Subject: Best app excellent many used
Body: Super. Most user friendly navigation app . Time saving .Emergancy help. Life saving . Perfect safety app.

Author: Needs to be fixed
Subject: Good
Body: I like that app. I just wish I would get all the notifications. I only get 30%??  I am not sure why. I have the notifications turned on.

Author: Victim102
Subject: Love it!
Body:
Waze has shown me alternative routes in areas I thought I knew. Time saver?
 “Big Time” 👍

Author: Techno///M
Subject: Not the fastest way
Body: I still use it for police alerts but keep getting frustrated because not only is the first route automatically selected not the fastest, but if I make a turn and it recalculates it is usually not the fastest way either. Many times the fastest way isn’t even an option in the list of three. Kind of defeats the purpose. I usually know how to get where I am going around town but is important I know the fastest way based on current conditions which is why I started using Waze. Seemed to do better before.

Author: Rouxt
Subject: GPS not working!
Body: Always no GPS and long time to get alternate route. Fix it!

Author: rbell
Subject: Best GPS
Body: We’ve compared Waze and Google Maps, and even though Google uses Waze, Waze works better. It does lead you down neighborhoods sometimes, which isn’t cool. And, living in LA, it tells you to turn left across 6 lanes in rush hour - not gonna happen. My one complaint is the most recent update slowed down my iPhone X a ton. Please fix this.

Author: kw tang
Subject: 交通圈
Body: 当我们要驶出交通圈的时候，不要叫我们去数第几个出口，有时数错就驾错去，驶出交通圈要像google map 那样，快要到出口的时候还会通知你说“驶出交通圈”，这样就会避免数错的问题！
Translated Body: When we want to get out of the traffic circle, do not ask us to go to the number of exits, sometimes mistakes go wrong, out of the traffic circle should be like google map, is about to exit when you are going to inform you that "driving Out of traffic circle ", so will avoid the wrong number of problems!

Author: Alexnfs06
Subject: Great app but needs more work
Body: I’ve been using waze for a year and it’s been great. But with the latest update the app has been going into a black screen and closing.

Subject: Poderia ser melhor!
Body: Tem muita propaganda, às vezes te manda por caminhos em áreas de risco( é necessário ter muito cuidado) e às vezes fica fazendo dar voltas por outras rotas sem necessidade, aliás acho que já foi melhor!
Translated Body: There is a lot of publicity, sometimes it leads you to roads in high risk areas (you have to be very careful) and sometimes you're doing some other routes without needing it, I think it's better already!

Author: DaniSndvl
Subject: Bueno pero no tanto
Body: Creo que el problema es cuando uno quiere aportar respecto a algunos tramos, ósea quise hacer un bloqueo por trabajos pero solamente me daba ciertas opciones, y estando al lado no pude hacerlo al final se envío uno erróneo, cuando trabajen más la aplicación podría resultar mucho más útil
Translated Body: I think the problem is when you want to contribute to some sections, I wanted to make a block for jobs but only gave me certain options, and being next I could not do it in the end sent the wrong one, when they work more the application could be a lot more useful
